videos.headline: Kansas State's Knowles takes off for 75-yard TD
videos.description: Malik Knowles dodges multiple Baylor defenders and weaves through traffic for a 75-yard Kansas State touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Kansas State’s Knowles takes off for 75-yard TD) 2020/11/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: Baylor's Sneed shows off his stepback on TD run
videos.description: R.J. Sneed hauls in a catch and stops on a dime to make his defender miss and then rushes to the end zone for a Baylor score vs. Kansas State.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Baylor’s Sneed shows off his stepback on TD run) 2020/11/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: Vaughn rushes down the middle for a 38-yard K-State touchdown
videos.description: Deuce Vaughn races his way through Baylor's defense and wins a footrace to the end zone to extend Kansas State's lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Vaughn rushes down the middle for a 38-yard K-State touchdown) 2020/11/28 ESHEET
